data.title: 100 Best Raw Milk Cheeses in Western Europe
data.meta_description: List includes: Grana Padano, Saint-Félicien, Queijo Serra da Estrela, Crottin de Chavignol, Reblochon.
data.text: TasteAtlas food rankings are based on the ratings of the TasteAtlas audience, with a series of mechanisms that recognize real users and that ignore bot, nationalist or local patriotic ratings, and give additional value to the ratings of users that the system recognizes as knowledgeable. For the “Top 100 Western European Raw Milk Cheeses” list until July 16, 2024, 12,064 ratings were recorded, of which 8,994 were recognized by the system as legitimate. TasteAtlas Rankings should not be seen as the final global conclusion about food. Their purpose is to promote excellent local foods, instill pride in traditional dishes, and arouse curiosity about dishes you haven’t tried.
